1
00:00:09,114 --> 00:00:13,160
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

2
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:17,800
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

3
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:22,840
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

4
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:28,000
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,415
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

6
00:00:32,415 --> 00:00:37,167
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

7
00:00:37,167 --> 00:00:42,400
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

8
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:47,853
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

9
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:55,760
=Rise Again=

10
00:00:56,144 --> 00:00:58,878
=Episode 13=

11
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:08,239
You can block one of my strikes.

12
00:01:08,519 --> 00:01:10,359
But can you block ten? A hundred?

13
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:19,719
Useless. Hurry up!

14
00:01:26,799 --> 00:01:27,920
So, you're done.

15
00:01:28,640 --> 00:01:29,519
Now it's my turn.

16
00:01:35,840 --> 00:01:37,079
Betraying your sect?

17
00:01:37,519 --> 00:01:38,680
Then I'll take your hands.

18
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:40,959
Serve evil?

19
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:42,239
Then I'll take your legs.

20
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:55,239
Su Wubing, you dare touch me?

21
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:57,319
I'm the Gu Group's heir.

22
00:01:57,439 --> 00:01:58,319
To deal with you,

23
00:01:59,239 --> 00:02:00,680
I don't even need to lift a finger.

24
00:02:01,319 --> 00:02:04,280
Take good care of your young master.

25
00:02:04,879 --> 00:02:06,319
- Yes, sir!
- Yes, sir!

26
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:11,120
Are you all insane?

27
00:02:11,639 --> 00:02:12,759
- Sorry, Mr. Gu.
- Sorry, Mr. Gu.

28
00:02:17,719 --> 00:02:19,240
Take your Mr. Gu

29
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:21,280
and get lost.

30
00:02:25,039 --> 00:02:25,840
And this one.

31
00:02:31,319 --> 00:02:32,560
Su Wubing, you!

32
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:33,680
Say no more, Mr. Gu.

33
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:35,280
Easy for you to say.

34
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:45,080
Thank you for your help.

35
00:02:49,319 --> 00:02:50,319
What are you waiting for?

36
00:02:50,599 --> 00:02:51,919
Say thank you.

37
00:02:55,599 --> 00:02:57,080
(How is Su Wubing this strong?)

38
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:58,520
(What level is he at?)

39
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,919
Hurry up.

40
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:09,080
Thank you.

41
00:03:11,319 --> 00:03:13,120
Mr. Shan, no need.

42
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:15,520
I was once part of the martial hall.

43
00:03:15,919 --> 00:03:17,439
Yingying has helped me a lot too.

44
00:03:18,439 --> 00:03:19,840
Helped you what?

45
00:03:20,719 --> 00:03:21,520
Shut up.

46
00:03:22,759 --> 00:03:25,039
Wubing, you're truly skilled.

47
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:27,439
Why not manage this martial hall

48
00:03:27,759 --> 00:03:29,360
with Yingying?

49
00:03:29,439 --> 00:03:30,520
I'm getting old.

50
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:32,400
Can't do it all myself anymore.

51
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:33,039
Dad!

52
00:03:33,039 --> 00:03:35,479
How can he run the hall with me?

53
00:03:35,759 --> 00:03:36,039
You...

54
00:03:36,039 --> 00:03:37,319
If that bothers you,

55
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:40,960
I'll become sworn brothers with him.

56
00:03:41,439 --> 00:03:43,400
From now on, he'll be your uncle.

57
00:03:44,599 --> 00:03:46,479
That way, it makes sense for him

58
00:03:47,199 --> 00:03:48,719
to be in charge with you.

59
00:03:49,199 --> 00:03:50,280
What...?

60
00:03:51,919 --> 00:03:52,759
Brother Wubing!

61
00:03:54,199 --> 00:03:56,319
Quick... call him Second Uncle.

62
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:59,039
I'm not calling him that!

63
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:02,120
Mr. Shan, no need for this.

64
00:04:02,439 --> 00:04:02,960
However...

65
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,879
Now I finally know

66
00:04:06,199 --> 00:04:08,560
where Yingying
gets her personality from.

67
00:04:09,919 --> 00:04:10,599
Su Wubing!

68
00:04:10,879 --> 00:04:12,240
Watch what you say.

69
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:12,759
Shut up.

70
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:14,919
Watch your tone with my brother.

71
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:19,959
Mr. Shan, it's fine.

72
00:04:20,439 --> 00:04:21,759
As long as Yingying

73
00:04:22,279 --> 00:04:24,720
doesn't embarrass me
in front of Ningxue.

74
00:04:26,240 --> 00:04:27,040
I'll take my leave.

75
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:29,720
Take care.

76
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,680
I didn't expect Wubing

77
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:36,279
to be this powerful.

78
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,639
You and him...

79
00:04:38,879 --> 00:04:40,759
There's nothing between us.

80
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:43,399
That's not what I meant.

81
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:44,759
With your skill level,

82
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,360
I know your limits.

83
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:49,519
You're no match for him.

84
00:04:51,519 --> 00:04:52,920
So I'm not good enough for him?

85
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:55,759
Are you even my dad?

86
00:04:58,439 --> 00:04:59,240
Unbelievable.

87
00:05:02,679 --> 00:05:05,045
(Shan Martial Hall)

88
00:05:14,959 --> 00:05:16,279
(The spiritual power is not enough.)

89
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:18,680
(If I break Ningxue's curse,)

90
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:20,399
(the Heavenly Dao will strike.)

91
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:23,560
(I must
regain Heavenly God Realm quickly.)

92
00:05:23,839 --> 00:05:25,319
(Then I can fight back.)

93
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:29,560
(I'll have to go find Ye Xiaonuan.)

94
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:42,720
You're early.

95
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:45,920
Dr. Su, I'm the patient.

96
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:47,439
Of course I'm anxious.

97
00:06:00,519 --> 00:06:02,160
(Too much spiritual power lost...)

98
00:06:02,759 --> 00:06:05,040
(The cold poison is striking back.)

99
00:06:33,399 --> 00:06:36,120
The Cold Marrow really works.

100
00:06:40,079 --> 00:06:40,959
What did you say?

101
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:44,439
Nothing.

102
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:47,720
Your cold poison

103
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:48,920
is almost gone.

104
00:06:49,319 --> 00:06:51,319
A few more treatments
and you'll recover.

105
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,839
Does this

106
00:06:56,439 --> 00:06:58,040
really blocks your sight?

107
00:07:04,079 --> 00:07:06,199
My Lord, Xiaonuan...

108
00:07:07,079 --> 00:07:07,879
Relax.

109
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:10,879
I refined most of her cold poison
last night.

110
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:13,680
She's much better now.

111
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:16,480
You've done so much for us.

112
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:19,519
I don't know how to thank you.

113
00:07:19,839 --> 00:07:21,079
Her pure yin body

114
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,839
helps me too.

115
00:07:23,959 --> 00:07:24,560
Then...

116
00:07:26,079 --> 00:07:27,439
the Holy Maiden's curse?

117
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:35,560
She has

118
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,279
less than two months.

119
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:39,199
And I...

120
00:07:40,839 --> 00:07:42,879
I still haven't reached
the Heavenly God Realm.

121
00:07:43,879 --> 00:07:45,399
I don't even know

122
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:46,920
where the Heavenly God Sword is.

123
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:51,199
Speaking of the Sword,

124
00:07:51,399 --> 00:07:53,199
I remember a place.

125
00:07:53,639 --> 00:07:54,639
Two Realms Mountain.

126
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:57,879
The Heavenly God Sword is there now.

127
00:07:58,439 --> 00:08:00,279
If you can make it

128
00:08:00,839 --> 00:08:02,199
to recognize you again,

129
00:08:02,639 --> 00:08:04,399
it might help you

130
00:08:04,399 --> 00:08:06,680
regain your Heavenly God Realm faster.

131
00:08:08,879 --> 00:08:09,920
Two Realms Mountain...

132
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:17,199
Why are you leaving?

133
00:08:17,199 --> 00:08:18,079
I still had things to say.

134
00:08:18,079 --> 00:08:18,839
Xiaonuan.

135
00:08:19,839 --> 00:08:21,480
Don't be rude to Wubing.

136
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:23,360
Grandpa.

137
00:08:23,879 --> 00:08:25,439
Why are you all so mysterious?

138
00:08:26,199 --> 00:08:27,279
You'll

139
00:08:27,839 --> 00:08:29,279
understand someday.

140
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:31,600
Tell me,

141
00:08:32,559 --> 00:08:34,799
do you like Su Wubing?

142
00:08:36,519 --> 00:08:39,120
I just think he's a good guy.

143
00:08:39,759 --> 00:08:41,480
What's wrong with that?

144
00:08:42,639 --> 00:08:44,080
Fair enough.

145
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:45,879
But

146
00:08:45,879 --> 00:08:48,440
he already has someone in his heart.

147
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:50,440
You'll need to step it up.

148
00:09:17,799 --> 00:09:18,600
Wubing...

149
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,600
Still awake?

150
00:09:22,279 --> 00:09:23,879
I was waiting for you.

151
00:09:24,279 --> 00:09:25,639
I need to talk.

152
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:28,879
I don't want to go back
to the Fang family.

153
00:09:29,279 --> 00:09:31,679
I want to stay here with you and Mom.

154
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:34,440
That's your real family.

155
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:36,919
You haven't seen them in years.

156
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:38,080
Don't you want to meet them?

157
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:39,919
I...

158
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:40,639
How about this.

159
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:42,759
Tomorrow I'll tell Mom

160
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:44,080
you're getting away

161
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:45,039
for a bit.

162
00:09:45,559 --> 00:09:46,200
Wubing...

163
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:48,480
I don't want to go.

164
00:09:51,879 --> 00:09:54,120
I know you only love Ningxue.

165
00:09:54,799 --> 00:09:57,799
I just want to stay by your side.

166
00:09:58,600 --> 00:09:59,919
That's all I want.

167
00:10:26,036 --> 00:10:30,139
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

168
00:10:30,139 --> 00:10:34,859
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

169
00:10:34,859 --> 00:10:39,739
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

170
00:10:39,739 --> 00:10:44,859
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

171
00:10:44,859 --> 00:10:49,259
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

172
00:10:49,259 --> 00:10:53,939
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

173
00:10:53,939 --> 00:10:59,339
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

174
00:10:59,339 --> 00:11:05,733
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪
